## 4. SelectionDAG Node Type System

**Location**: llvm/include/llvm/CodeGen/SelectionDAG.h, llvm/lib/CodeGen/SelectionDAG/SelectionDAG.cpp

SelectionDAG nodes use EVT to track value types:
- Each SDNode has value types in SDVTList
- SDValue wraps (SDNode*, ResNo) and provides `.getValueType()` returning EVT
- Type information flows through DAG optimization and legalization passes

SelectionDAG provides EVT-aware helpers:
```cpp
